Well, i have remade my 1st trap hallway map:

-It' s surely improved, It's bigger and I have added several traps (about 8), light effects, sparks, sounds, props, etc.

-Also I added ct and t spawns, so now 36 of total players can play the map... =D 
(yust to make sure it can't get full)

-In my previus map you started with a gun.. (i didn' t quite know how to put only knife start). 
That has all been fixed. 

-The map is covered in graffitis and posters, yust to give it some look =D...

-That' s all.. hope you download my map, cuz I'm sure you will like it. =P
